Presto is a Hypermedia-driven generic editing framework. It consists of an SPI for data providers and a HTTP interface for retrieving and updating information. The APIs are fully quite stable, but will need maturing before considered final.

==Features==

* Hypermedia driven generic editing.
* Multiple data providers available (CouchDB and Ontopia).
* JSON over HTTP using Hypermedia implemented in Java/JAX-RS.

